column1: ## (1) pmId. Promoter identifier assigned by RegulonDB
## (3) strand. DNA strand where the promoter is located
## (4) posTSS. Genome map position of Transcription Start Site (+1)
## (5) sigmaFactor. Sigma Factor that recognize the promoter
## (7) firstGeneName. Name of the first gene of promoter
## (8) distToFirstGene. distance to first gene of promoter
## (9) pmEvidence. Evidence that supports the existence of the promoter
## (11) confidenceLevel. Promoter confidence level (Values: Confirmed, Strong, Weak)
